title: 257: Divisional Round Preview
itunes:title: 257: Divisional Round Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks get you ready for the second round of the NFL Playoffs by breaking down the biggest matchups and picking a few upsets along the way (8:58). The guys also give you x-factors for the divisional round (26:21) and preview the free agency market (33:31).
